<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Quote Request Received - Genfix</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .content { background: #fff; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #dee2e6; border-radius: 8px; }
    .footer { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #6c757d; text-align: center; }
    .highlight { background: #e3f2fd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 15px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>ðŸŽ‰ Quote Request Received!</h1>
      <p>Thank you for choosing Genfix</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p><%= @greeting %>,</p>

      <p>Thank you for your quote request! We've received your details and our team will prepare a customized quote for you.</p>

      <div class="highlight">
        <h3>Your Request Details:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Equipment:</strong> <%= @quote_request.equipment_type %></li>
          <li><strong>Rental Duration:</strong> <%= @quote_request.rental_duration %></li>
          <li><strong>Delivery Address:</strong> <%= @quote_request.delivery_address %></li>
          <% if @quote_request.special_requirements.present? %>
            <li><strong>Special Requirements:</strong> <%= @quote_request.special_requirements %></li>
          <% end %>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p><strong>What happens next?</strong></p>
      <ol>
        <li>Our power specialist will review your requirements</li>
        <li>We'll prepare a customized quote (usually within 1 hour)</li>
        <li>You'll receive an email with your quote details</li>
        <li>If approved, we'll arrange delivery and setup</li>
      </ol>

      <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to call us on <strong>0412 345 678</strong>.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>
      The Genfix Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Genfix - Powering Brisbane Since 2020<br>
      Email: info@genfix.com | Phone: 0412 345 678</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>